dataset.title: FRTIB Financial Statements
dataset.description: These reports provide annual statements on net assets available for benefits, outlines changes to the net assets available, and includes an independent auditor’s findings on the report. Financial statements are provided in PDF format which includes both financial tables and written explanations of the data included.

dataset.title: Share Price Data
dataset.description: Periodic reviews of plan offering competitiveness and share acquisition pricing is available via FRTIB’s Open Data Plan. Available data includes share price data in CSV format and third-party competitiveness assessments in PDF format with included financial data in tables and graphs. Share price data is updated daily and is available at https://www.tsp.gov/InvestmentFunds/FundPerformance/index.html

dataset.title: Participant Survey Reports
dataset.description: The FRTIB conducts recurring surveys of the participants in the plan to help shape the future of the Plan. Aggregated analysis of the surveys is published public via as part of FRTIB’s Open Data Plan. Reports are in PDF format with included data tables.

dataset.title: FOIA Information
dataset.description: Frequently requested record, Chief FOIA Officer Reports, FOIA Quarterly Reports, and annual FOIA Reports are all available from FRTIB. Reports are available in a range of formats, including machine-readable XML files.
